, the Guianas, and Amazon and Atlantic coast of 
<collectingCountry box="[2106,2185,822,855]" name="Brazil" pageId="56" pageNumber="540">Brazil</collectingCountry>
(N 
<collectingRegion box="[2243,2447,822,855]" country="Brazil" name="Espirito Santo" pageId="56" pageNumber="540">Espirito Santo</collectingRegion>
